    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>[Congressional Record Volume 163, Number 160 (Thursday, October 5, 2017)]From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. MESSER:H.R. 3982.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Article I, Section 8[Page H7888]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
